channel.description:
- SUBSCRIBE-  
FOR PREDICTIONS THAT MAY AFFECT YOU
#Prv.22:3 A PRUDENT man forseeth evil and hideth himself. The  SIMPLE pass on and are PUNISHED
#1Jhn.4:7 ...he that KNOWETH GOD, HEARETH US; he that is NOT OF GOD, HEARETH NOT US, hereby know we the spirit of TRUTH, and the spirit of ERROR

To Prophesy Accurately -RECEIVE CHRIST
-BIBLE(Ps.36:9)
-CHURCH(Ps.73:17)
-FAST & PRAY(Jr.33:3)
-HOLINESS(Ps.25:14)
-SPIRIT FILLED(Lk.1:67)
-WORSHIP(Ex.15:20)
Nothing More! No divination-palm reading-incense-candle burning, fortune telling, hypnosis, new age, mysticism, nostrodamos, seance, channeling, rapture-date, scientology, voodoo, astrology, psychicism, spiritism, mediumship, meditating, horoscopy, necromancy, numerology, feast days numbering, ancestry, animism, angelology, naturopathy, idolatry, pluralism. They failed to predict the QUAKES in Haiti, Chile, New Zealand, Japan; Floods in Pakistan, Australia. They are useless & dangerous. (Is.8:19-21; Is.44:25; Hos.4:12-13; Is.47:9; Ez.7:18-19)
